{"tid":1127362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六晏就一點後裝修有冇得投訴?","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T07:14:36.000Z","uid":143953,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a075fad335ce1e8dcce17bf5310a46d0fc64aa14","tid":1127362,"uid":143953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"見有人話星期六得朝早9點到晏就1點<br />\n但係自己查又見唔到咩地方有講<br />\n想問下有冇得投訴 同向邊到投訴最有效<br />\n今朝已經同管理處講左<br />\n到依加都仲揼緊同鑽野<br />\n比樓上搞到成日都冇覺好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd877685a1b6bc9081166a3343fa8822d39a744","tid":1127362,"uid":165510,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"有啲撚屌好撚黑人憎<br />\n假期9點幾開始鑽野 人地唔撚使訓 淨係佢屋企要裝修<br />\n屌佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58afd15abbc66b262604209462a3a99bb90eac3","tid":1127362,"uid":196484,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"咁多要求住半山呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b6d9eccb050e964d962dc283e993be0eb6fc3d","tid":1127362,"uid":143953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd877685a1b6bc9081166a3343fa8822d39a744","tid":1127362,"uid":165510,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"有啲撚屌好撚黑人憎<br />\n假期9點幾開始鑽野 人地唔撚使訓 淨係佢屋企要裝修<br />\n屌佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"我樓上就係<br />\n唔止 平日都嘈"},{"pid":"c29581814fdcf70559ed0068db50ccb7bfae4a1a","tid":1127362,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0112ca7d47e7f7e078e08fd8f9709c0fe034dfe7","tid":1127362,"ui